You may say so.

89
00:06:18,912 --> 00:06:21,310
那么下周我去伦敦时  你就放个假吧
Take off when I'm in London next week.

90
00:06:22,332 --> 00:06:24,157
车子也借给你用
I tell you what, you take the car.

91
00:06:24,417 --> 00:06:27,243
-那辆老戴姆勒  -先生  我不能接受
-Take the Daimler. -Good Lord, sir, I couldn't.

92
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:31,789
