Sorry.

105
00:07:12,340 --> 00:07:15,208
知道我最喜欢英国报纸什么地方吗
You know what I like best about your papers?

106
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,126
这些讣告
These obituaries.

107
00:07:17,637 --> 00:07:20,463
无论什么样的混蛋都能得到很体面的葬礼讣文
Every son of a gun gets this stately funeral oration.

108
00:07:20,723 --> 00:07:23,883
-美国可没有这东西  -确实  先生
-It's not an art we have in the States. -Indeed, sir.

109
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,969
谢谢  史蒂文斯
Thank you, Stevens.

110
00:07:27,689 --> 00:07:28,763
刘易斯先生
Mr. Lewis.

111
