116
00:08:25,163 --> 00:08:29,407
贝恩夫人  你一直有非常好的记忆力
Mrs. Benn, I always said you possess an amazing memory.

117
00:08:29,667 --> 00:08:32,660
府邸的新主人确实是国会议员刘易斯
Our new employer is indeed Congressman Lewis

118
00:08:32,921 --> 00:08:35,997
